➜宽哥：《一斛珠》
http://www.sohu.com/a/415792401_100115135	38716
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/c10c17f6b7514e6f9a36807b4452aaf4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《一斛珠》（词林正韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋光渐暮，幽幽梦里乡关路。古楼旧巷行经处，锦瑟年华，笑语欢无数。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逝水无情留不住，雅文精武两耽误。不辞醽醁花间赋。菊蕊东篱，但识琴中趣。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/3d92b18fa1934b0da90e23549a2e3c03.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/2b19c2c9723d418aa6541a91f1845191.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
