<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/295e3c37420f4803855c89af37608fea.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">（诗人木子作画图）</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝：绘花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">彼岸花儿悄，飞鸿托信忙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">邀君千万里，共赏一支芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欲把芳心诉，芊芊玉指摇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">娇枝香玉露，月下共良宵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/2d4772e32a184150a77ac030bcc1e1bf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝：花</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
