<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/辉哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轻枝三两俏，花朵秀清芬；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋日迎风舞，仿如在盛春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>美人花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">娟花三朵俏，嫩叶满枝柔；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心事因时动，风来正入秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/1eae6efeb2eb4b0b9c9cad3162c63989.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.女人花（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柔情缕缕长，化作女儿香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只愿君心久，何愁不盛妆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.无名花（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思念万般痴，为君守一枝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘多少意？脉脉两相知。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200831/80886c5984e0457c88117fded7c2fc85.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝：纸上花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花开三两朵，情事几思量。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纸上多心意，为君独自芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（诗友雅和）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/1dd8e1363ef144e6aba3f02f643d32bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
